title: Italy 20 Year bond Yield
description: Italy 20 Year Bond Yield was 4.64 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Italy 20 Year bond Yield reached an all time high of 8.16 in November of 2011. This page includes a chart with historical data for Italy 20Y.
author: Dipartimento del Tesoro
